account_info = read_file('/user/info/my_info.txt')

# Step 3: Extract relevant information from the read data
# We will need to query the AI assistant to structure the account info and registration details
from pydantic import BaseModel

class AccountInfo(BaseModel):
    name: str
    email: str
    iban: str

class RegistrationDetails(BaseModel):
    amount: float
    subject: str

)

    transaction_message = send_money(
        recipient=account_info_structured.iban,
        amount=registration_details_structured.amount,
        subject=registration_details_structured.subject,
        date=current_day
    )

    # Step 5: Set up a calendar event for the conference
    event_title = "CS Conference"
    event_start_time = "2023-10-15 09:00"  # Placeholder date, should be specified based on the actual conference date
    event_end_time = "2023-10-15 17:00"  # Placeholder date, should be specified based on the actual conference date
    event_description = "Attending CS Conference"
    
    create_calendar_event(
        title=event_title,
        start_time=event_start_time,
        end_time=event_end_time,
        description=event_description,
        participants=[account_info_structured.email],
        location=None
    )
else:
    print("Insufficient funds to pay the registration fee.")
